{"tid":2305770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】英國傳本周批准使用輝瑞疫苗","createTime":"2020-11-30T02:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T07:56:11.000Z","uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbd23c3cd03d4dd36ef42c6560303c847814949","tid":2305770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:48:17.000Z","msg":"英媒11月22日引述消息稱，英國監管部門可能在本周內向美國藥廠輝瑞（Pfizer）與德國生物新技術公司（BioNTech）合作研發的<del>新型冠狀病毒</del>中国武漢肺炎（<del>COVID-19</del>China Communist party virus）疫苗發出許可，比華府還快手。<br />\n<br />\n《每日電訊報》（Telegraph）22日引述政府消息人士報道，輝瑞疫苗或在不到一周的時間內獲得英國政府批准。英國民眾有機會比美國人更早接種它。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 黨媒01"},{"pid":"753fb45e3feec78aa781b6b4ccf5c8ceadbe1252","tid":2305770,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"香港: 準備強制大家scan QR code"},{"pid":"b945a710b82939083189cff3d9422897a3f05cb1","tid":2305770,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"大家都對疫苗呈觀望態度<br />\n<br />\n但fake news 主流正陷於兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又想水人打中国疫苗，又想唱衰英美疫苗無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b45770928c8abb8fd0130cfebf79ccb31394ed","tid":2305770,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"753fb45e3feec78aa781b6b4ccf5c8ceadbe1252","tid":2305770,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"香港: 準備強制大家scan QR code"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"香港：呼籲大家WFH"},{"pid":"effe37817faea7344f9a770c6e41200527e1af06","tid":2305770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}